// rect_matmul: C = A @ B  (M×K @ K×N → M×N f32).
// 64×64 tile, 256 thr (8 simdgroups 4×2), BK=16, double-buffered.
// Padded threadgroup memory (LDA=20, LDB=68) to avoid bank conflicts.
